{"TopicId":48513,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Possibility of Portal 3","CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-15T19:53:49Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-15T19:53:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf Portal 3 were to be released, how would the story play out? Post your ideas here\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-15T20:02:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ETimewise it wouldn\u0027t have to take place \u003Cem\u003Eafter\u003C/em\u003E Portal 2, especially if they\u0027re using a different character.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr Shifty","CreatedById":68146,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-15T20:13:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI expect that Portal 3 will be released approximately \u002212 months\u0022 (in Valve time) after Half Life 3 is released. In other words, your great-grandchildren may have a chance to play it before they get too old to hold a controller.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuperWeegee4000","CreatedById":71621,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-15T20:31:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI honestly think Portal 3 would be too much of a stretch to be a good idea. The series had a great run, and another game could detract from the experience.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sylandro","CreatedById":80729,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-15T21:05:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf it was released, i\u0027m hoping it will take place before Portal 1 and Portal 2.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf so, that means we can hear more of Cave Johnson\u0027s priceless quotes.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketTurtle","CreatedById":67534,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-15T21:28:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sylandro\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sylandro\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Eif it was released, i\u0027m hoping it will take place before portal 1 and portal 2.\u003Cp\u003EIf so, that means we can hear more of cave johnson\u0027s priceless quotes.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E^^This.^^^\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-16T01:04:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think they could elaborate on the old underground facility in Portal II. The \u0022quantum tunneling device\u0022, instead of the A.S.H.P.D. would be interesting.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shoveycat","CreatedById":71091,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-16T01:17:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027d like to see the test facility in its prime, Cave Johnson, dirty hobos pooping coal, and $60 in all\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bioman222","CreatedById":30364,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-16T01:40:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI don\u0027t give a Sh*t about the story! I want test chambers.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003ENOOOOWWWW!!1!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bioman222","CreatedById":30364,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-16T01:40:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m just kidding, BTW.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LaydeeDem","CreatedById":5984,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-16T02:13:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bioman222\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Bioman222\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI don\u0027t give a Sh*t about the story! I want test chambers.\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003ENOOOOWWWW!!1!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMake your own!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/b7rZO2ACP3A?feat